Package: disclosuR
Type: Package
Title: Text Conversion from Nexis Uni PDFs to R Data Frames
Version: 0.0.1.0
Date: 2023-04-19
Author: Jonas Roettger
Maintainer: Jonas Roettger <jonas.roettger@gmx.net>
Description: Functions to transform newswire and earnings call transcripts as PDFs obtained from Nexis Uni to R data frames. Various newswires and FairDisclosure earnings call formats are supported. 
License: GPL-3
Imports: dplyr, lubridate, pdftools, qdap, SentimentAnalysis, stringi, stringr, syuzhet, zoo, SnowballC, tm
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
